    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the approved assessment plan. The computational model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump at the specified model risk level.",
